      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "は、早いな……まだ朝の七時前なのに……\n今開けるからちょっと待ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-You're up early… It's not even seven yet…\nI'll open the door now‚ just give me a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3126.417223599999,
          "startTime": 12.5597505569
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.5597505569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、ビーチに行きましょう！\n楽しみで楽しみで仕方なくって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's go to the beach!\nI'm so excited‚ I can hardly wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8440417169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待ってくれ、朝食もまだなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait a minute‚ I haven't even had breakfast yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0930844624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.8456696668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな～。三十分前にはもう\n朝食のビュッフェ始まってますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no~. The breakfast buffet started\nthirty minutes ago!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.3123363334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ついさっき起きたばかりなんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just woke up a moment ago…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.1790030001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.6591406184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　す、すみません……！\n私、張り切り過ぎちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? I-I'm sorry…!\nI got a bit too hyped up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4924739518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.6591406184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、朝ご飯が終わったら\n待ち合わせでいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about we see\nafter breakfast?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7924739518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、一時間後にビーチの入り口で待ち合わせよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ let's meet at the beach entrance in an hour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6924739518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.770456886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！\nじゃあ、それまで少し、近くを散歩してます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it!\nUntil then‚ I'll take a short walk nearby.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2037902193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.7037902193
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まだ朝早いから大丈夫か……\nあまり遠くまで一人で行かないでくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's still early in the morning‚ are you sure you'll be okay?\nDon't go too far by yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1000026703,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10082.311502799996,
          "startTime": 64.1823141731
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "どこで遊ぶか下調べしておきますね！\nすっごく楽しみです！　それでは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll scout out the best places to play!\nI'm so excited! See you later!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4156480786,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5338.325759,
          "startTime": 65.7539738376
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.515646807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、もの凄く楽しみにしてるな\n……よし、俺もひと肌脱ぐか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire's really looking forward to this.\n…Alright‚ guess I'll get ready too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9333316803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――一時間後",
