    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、お待たせ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ sorry to keep you waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8044946029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.8313839589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　お疲れ様です！\nって、あれ……その格好は……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Thank you for your hard work!\nOh‚ um… What's with that outfit…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7647144949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "すみれが楽しみにしているみたいだったからな\n俺もいろいろ準備してきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you seemed really excited about it‚ so…\nI also prepared various things for this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9666624706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.261746692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "わ～！　シュノーケルを付けて、浮き輪まではめて\nもう楽しむ気満々って感じ、です、けど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! With snorkel and float already on…\nYou seem all set for fun‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.450118683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.461746692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "なんでスーツ姿なんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you in a suit…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.461746692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "水着だけ借りられなくてな\nこんなことになってしまった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Couldn't just rent a swimsuit.\nIt turned out like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1999958039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.5271436367
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど、それならオフィス街のど真ん中で\n夏を満喫しそうな格好も納得……なっ……ふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I see. In that case‚ it makes sense to enjoy summer right\nin the middle of the office district… Ahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.1271408393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.3271436367
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "あははっ、だ、だからって、スーツにシュノーケルで\n浮き輪までっ、さすがに変ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha! But still‚ wearing a suit with snorkel and float…\nIt's a bit strange‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.193807506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなに笑うことないだろ\nスーツでも気分は上がると思うし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-don't laugh that much.\nI think even in a suit‚ your mood will improve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2999958039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
